2B%20parks%20in%20southern%20Africa%2C%20including%20Kruger.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Wild%20Card%20is%20discounted%20for%20South%20Africans%20but%20it%20cost%20me%203%2C780%20rands%2C%20or%20about%20%24200%2C%20as%20a%20foreigner.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWithout%20a%20Wild%20Card%2C%20I%20would've%20had%20to%20pay%20over%20486%20rands%20a%20day%20to%20visit%20Kruger%2C%20meaning%20this%20pass%20pays%20for%20itself%20in%20just%20over%20a%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOverall%2C%20my%20pass%20came%20to%20about%20270%20rands%20a%20day%20for%20the%20two-week%20trip.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22ff79ae5c-f453-4f80-baca-61220a0f5ed2%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EWe%20also%20stayed%20in%20one%20of%20Kruger's%20many%20rest%20camps%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20most%20immersive%20ways%20to%20experience%20Kruger%20is%20by%20camping%20in%20the%20South%20African%20bush.%20We%20saw%20elephants%20near%20our%20camp%20and%20woke%20up%20to%20the%20sounds%20of%20warthogs%20and%20hyenas%20in%20the%20distance.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsurprising-things-moving-to-south-africa-from-us-2022-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elive%20in%20South%20Africa%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20so%20it%20was%20easy%20enough%20to%20bring%20our%20own%20camping%20gear%2C%20though%20travelers%20can%20rent%20a%20tent%2C%20sleeping%20bags%2C%20chairs%2C%20and%20cooking%20basics%20from%20nearby%20rental%20companies%20for%20a%20few%20thousand%20rands%20for%20two%20weeks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKruger%20National%20Park%20has%20a%20range%20of%20rest%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fglamping-below-freezing-temperatures-winter-review-photos-2023%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecamps%20for%20different%20budgets%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20preferences%2C%20whether%20you%20prefer%20to%20use%20your%20own%20tent%20or%20stay%20in%20a%20bungalow%20with%20your%20own%20kitchen%20and%20bathroom.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPrices%20also%20vary%20depending%20on%20the%20season%2C%20so%20it's%20wise%20to%20avoid%20really%20busy%20months%2C%20like%20September%20and%20December.%20I%20found%20that%20around%20mid-January%20to%20mid-March%2C%20two%20people%20can%20camp%20at%20Punda%20Maria%2C%20one%20of%20Kruger's%20cheapest%20camping%20options%2C%20for%20just%20285%20rands%20a%20night.%20During%20high%20season%2C%20prices%20go%20up%20by%20about%20100%20rands%20per%20night.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20husband%20and%20I%20visited%20during%20a%20less%20busy%20season.%20We%20camped%20at%20Maroela%20Satellite%20Camp%20and%20Crocodile%20Bridge%20Rest%20Camp%20for%20331%20to%20349%20rands%20a%20night.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22c9b3a8c8-2f80-47b2-af3d-dfb173bd1f05%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ECooking%20our%20own%20food%20saved%20us%20money%20%E2%80%A6%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20chose%20to%20prepare%20our%20own%20meals%20and%20braai%20(a%20type%20of%20South%20African%20barbecue)%20beneath%20the%20stars.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFortunately%2C%20most%20campsites%20have%20plug%20points%2C%20braai%20stands%2C%20shared%20bathrooms%2C%20shared%20kitchens%2C%20and%20shops%20selling%20everything%20you%20need%20to%20braai.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20park%20also%20has%20restaurants%20and%20coffee%20shops%20scattered%20throughout%20it%2C%20which%20is%20helpful%20for%20anyone%20who%20wants%20to%20purchase%20food%20and%20drinks%20without%20leaving%20the%20property.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20there's%20nothing%20quite%20like%20braaiing%20beneath%20the%20stars%2C%20watching%20for%20the%20occasional%20hyena%20along%20the%20fence%20line.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22a4f9b2c3-0e93-488a-9ce6-923233a9f7c6%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%A6%20and%20so%20did%20doing%20a%20self-driving%20safari%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221280%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22car%20with%20boar%20walking%20behind%20it%20in%20safari%20in%20South%20Africa%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6644ed749fc063e829b15329%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20heig