6quot%3BI%20think%20all%20the%20guys%20throughout%20the%20season%20played%20phenomenal%20cricket.%20There%20was%20a%20little%20bit%20of%20fatigue%20at%20the%20back%20end%2C%20but%20it%20doesn't%20matter%20when%20you're%20in%20games%20like%20this.%20You%20gotta%20turn%20up%20and%20perform.%26quot%3B%20Chasing%20a%20target%20of%20176%2C%20RR%20were%2065%20for%20two%20by%20the%20eighth%20over%2C%20but%20kept%20on%20losing%20wickets%20in%20clusters%20thereafter%2C%20leading%20to%20their%20downfall.%20Commenting%20on%20the%20defeat%2C%C2%A0Sangakkara%C2%A0felt%20the%20middle-order%20could%20have%20done%20better.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20was%20just%20a%20case%20of%20being%20smart%20and%20keeping%20our%20composure.%20Unfortunately%2C%20when%20you%20lose%20wickets%20in%20clusters%2C%20it%20becomes%20hard%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEven%20in%20the%20RCB%20chase%2C%20if%20you%20lose%20wickets%2C%20it%20gets%20tense%20and%20close.%20Unfortunately%2C%20we%20needed%20a%20little%20bit%20more%20from%20our%20middle-order.%26quot%3B%20RR%20were%20also%20without%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Jos%20Buttler%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F1367-jos-buttler-playerprofile%5C%22%3EJos%20Buttler%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20who%20has%20been%20a%20force%20for%20the%20team%20in%20the%20top%20order.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%C2%A0Sangakkara%C2%A0said%20that%20international%20scheduling%20was%20something%20that%20they%20couldn't%20control%2C%20he%20felt%20that%20other%20batters%20should%20have%20stepped%20up.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20always%20say%20that%20the%20best%20ability%20is%20availability%2C%20and%20unfortunately%2C%20we%20lost%20Jos.%20He%20is%20a%20big%20loss%2C%20without%20a%20doubt%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20you're%20in%20a%20playoff%20like%20this%2C%20and%20you've%20got%20that%20start%20without%20Jos%2C%20we%20expect%20the%20other%20batters%20to%20also%20step%20up.%26quot%3B%20RR