tch%20up%20financially.%20It's%20not%20just%20the%20holiday%20gifts%2C%20meals%2C%20parties%2C%20outfits%2C%20and%20decorations.%20It's%20also%20the%20looming%20deadline%20for%20getting%20the%20most%20out%20of%20your%20tax%20deductions%2C%20like%20donations%20to%20non-profits%20and%20contributions%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fbest-ira-accounts%5C%22%3EIRA%20accounts%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EComing%20up%20with%20thousands%20of%20dollars%20at%20the%20end%20of%20the%20year%20is%20something%20I'm%20giving%20up%20in%202024.%20It%20is%20too%20stressful%20and%20draws%20down%20our%20emergency%20fund%20too%20much%20at%20an%20already%20expensive%20time%20of%20year.%20Instead%2C%20I'm%20using%20the%20second%20half%20of%20the%20year%20to%20get%20ahead%2C%20which%20means%20doing%20three%20things%20starting%20this%20summer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E1.%20We%20have%20an%20account%20just%20for%20year-end%20contributions%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20partner%20and%20I%20are%20creating%20an%20account%20just%20for%20funding%20our%20IRAs%20and%20for%20donations%20at%20year-end.%20Deposits%20to%20the%20account%20come%20from%20our%20discretionary%20pool%20of%20money%2C%20so%20we%20are%20not%20short-changing%20any%20bills%2C%20savings%2C%20or%20our%20much-needed%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fwhat-is-an-emergency-fund%5C%22%3Eemergency%20fund%3C%2Fa%3E.%20This%20year%2C%20our%20microwave%2C%20washer-dryer%20combo%2C%20oven%2C%20and%20tires%20all%20blew%20out%20at%20about%20the%20same%20time%20%E2%80%94%20a%20perfect%20example%20of%20why%20an%20emergency%20fund%20is%20critical%20in%20our%20household.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnother%20way%20we%20stay%20organized%20all%20year%20is%20to%20keep%20a%20large%20manila%20envelope%20and%20put%20the%20receipt%20in%20the%20envelope%20when%20we%20purchase%20or%20do%20anything%20that%20is%20deductible.%20This%20practice%20of%20maintaining%20receipts%20would%20come%20in%