hwi-yadav-slams-pm-modi-accuses-him-of-trying-to-end-reservation%2Farticleshow%2F110423045.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22PM's%20%26quot%3BMujra%26quot%3B%20Attack%20On%20INDIA%20Bloc%2C%20Priyanka%20Gandhi's%20%26quot%3BDecorum%26quot%3B%20Reply%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EPrime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi's%20%26quot%3Bmujra%26quot%3B%20remark%20at%20a%20rally%20in%20Bihar%20today%20drew%20a%20sharp%20response%20from%20Congress%20leader%20Priyanka%20Gandhi%20Vadra%2C%20who%20said%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20must%20maintain%20the%20decorum%20of%20his%20post.%20The%20remark%2C%20made%20when%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20was%20accusing%20the%20Opposition%20of%20vote%20bank%20politics%2C%20was%20panned%20by%20other%20INDIA%20leaders%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMujra%20is%20a%20dance%20performance%20widely%20associated%20with%20courtesans.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAddressing%20a%20rally%20in%20Bihar%2C%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20doubled%20down%20on%20his%20charge%20that%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%20plans%20to%20rob%20backward%20classes%20of%20their%20rights%20and%20favour%20Muslims%20--%20an%20allegation%20denied%20by%20the%20Congress%20and%20its%20allies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBihar%20is%20the%20land%20which%20has%20given%20a%20new%20direction%20to%20the%20fight%20for%20social%20justice.%20I%20wish%20to%20declare%20on%20its%20soil%20that%20I%20will%20foil%20the%20plans%20of%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%20to%20rob%20SCs%2C%20STs%20and%20OBCs%20of%20their%20rights%20and%20divert%20these%20to%20Muslims.%20They%20may%20remain%20enslaved%20and%20perform%20'mujra'%20to%20please%20their%20vote%20bank%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20said%20the%20people%20of%20Bihar%20have%20been%20hurt%20by%20remarks%20against%20migrants%20allegedly%20made%20by%20leaders%20of%20the%20Congress%20in%20Punjab%20and%20Telangana%2C%20DMK%20in%20Tamil%20Nadu%20and%20Trinamool%20Congress%20in%20West%20Bengal.%20In%20another%20%26quot%3Bmujra%20jab%26quot%3B%20targeting%20the%20Tejashwi%20Yadav-led%20RJD%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThese%20RJD%20people%20who%20keep%20doing%20'mujra'%20with%20their%20lantern%20(poll%20symbol)%20do%20not%20have%20the%20courage%20to%20speak%20a%20word%20in%20protest.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Prime%20Minister%20went%20on%20to%20say%20that%20the%20Opposition%20parties%20will%20change%20the%20Constitution%20if%20they%20are%20voted%20to%20power%20--%20a%20charge%20earlier%20levelled%20by%20the%20Congress%20on%20the%20ruling%20BJP.%C2%A0%26quot%3BIf%20they%20are%20voted%20to%20power%2C%20the%20first%20thing%20they%20would%20do%20is%20to%20change%20the%20Constitution%20so%20that%20even%20the%20court%20is%20unable%20to%20overrule%20their%20attempts%20to%20divert%20reservations%20to%20Muslims.%20I%20have%20been%20challenging%20them%20to%20refute%20me%20in%20writing%2C%20but%20they%20have%20been%20reluctant%20because%20they%20have%20a%20guilty%20conscience%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStressing%20that%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%20is%20headed%20for%20a%20defeat%20in%20the%20ongoing%20general%20election%2C%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BWhen%20the%20results%20are%20out%2C%20RJD%20and%20Congress%20workers%20will%20be%20seen%20tearing%20off%20each%20other's%20clothes.%20The%20royal%20family%20of%20the%20Congress%20will%20put%20the%20entire%20blame%20of%20defeat%20on%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge%20and%20leave%20for%20holiday%20abroad%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHitting%20back%2C%20Ms%20Gandhi%20Vadra%20said%20no%20Prime%20Minister%20would%20have%20used%20such%20language.%20%26quot%3BWhat%20is%20Modiji%20saying%3F%20Is%20it%20not%20his%20responsibility%20to%20maintain%20the%20decorum%20of%20his%20post%3F%20We%20respect%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20post.%20His%20reality%20can%20now%20be%20seen.%20Do%20not%20show%20so%20much%20reality%20to%20the%20country.%20He%20has%20forgotten%20that%20he%20represents%20th