the%20EC%20to%20compile%20and%20publish%20this%20data%20on%20its%20website%20after%20each%20phase%2C%20beginning%20with%20the%20next%20round%20of%20voting%20in%20the%202024%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20EC%20feels%20duly%20strengthened%20by%20the%20Supreme%20Court's%20observations%20and%20verdict%20on%20the%20process%20of%20release%20of%20turnout%20data%2C%20the%20poll%20body%20said%20in%20a%20statement%20today%20while%20voting%20was%20going%20on%20in%20the%20sixth%20phase.%20The%20final%20phase%20is%20on%20June%201.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20brings%20upon%20the%20Commission%2C%20a%20higher%20responsibility%20to%20serve%20the%20cause%20of%20electoral%20democracy%20with%20undeterred%20resolution%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20EC%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3ECommission%20releases%20absolute%20number%20of%20voters%20for%20all%20completed%20phases%20of%20General%20Elections%202024%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnDetails%20%3A%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2Fz0QVHGM41Z%5C%22%3Ehttps%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2Fz0QVHGM41Z%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Spokesperson%20ECI%20(%40SpokespersonECI)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSpokespersonECI%2Fstatus%2F1794317350227136897%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EMay%2025%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20EC%20said%20the%20whole%20exercise%20of%20release%20of%20turnout%20data%20from%20the%20day%20elections%20began%20on%20April%2019%20has%20been%20accurate%2C%20consistent%20and%20in%20accordance%20with%20election%20laws%20and%20%26quot%3Bwithout%20any%20discrepancy%20whatsoever%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20EC%20refuted%20allegations%20about%20delay%20in%20releasing%20voter%20turnout%20data.%20It%20said%20the%20data%20was%20always%20available%2024x7%20on%20the%20%26quot%3Bfacilitative%20voter%20turnout%20app%20from%209.30%20am%20on%20the%20polling%20day%20in%20each%20phase%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20(app)%20publishes%20estimated%20voter%20turnout%20on%20two%20hourly%20basis%20till%201730%20hours%20(5.30%20pm).%20After%201900%20hours%20(7%20pm)%20when%20the%20polling%20parties%20start%20arriving%2C%20data%20is%20continuously%20updated.%20By%20midnight%20on%20the%20poll%20day%2C%20the%20voter%20turnout%20app%20will%20show%20best%20estimated%20%26quot%3BClose%20of%20Poll%20(COP)%26quot%3B%20data%20in%20percentage%20form%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20EC%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDifferent%20media%20organisations%20pick%20up%20data%20at%20different%20points%20in%20time%20as%20per%20their%20convenience%20to%20report%20next%20morning.%20After%20the%20arrival%20of%20the%20poll%20parties%2C%20depending%20on%20geographical%20and%20weather%20conditions%2C%20the%20data%20of%20voters%20attains%20finality%20on%20P%2B1%20or%20P%2B2%20or%20P%2B3%20(p%20denotes%20polling%20day)%20or%20more%20days%2C%20depending%20upon%20arrival%20of%20parties%20and%20number%20of%20re-polls%2C%20if%20any%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20EC%20said%20in%20the%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ciframe%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.scribd.com%2Fembeds%2F735964602%2Fcontent%3Fstart_page%3D1%26view_mode%3Dscroll%26access_key%3Dkey-XM65tR1OBgrstTNSmuEY%5C%22%20data-auto-height%3D%5C%22false%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22650%5C%22%20data-aspect-ratio%3D%5C%220.7729220222793488%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Absolute%20Number%20Of%20Voters%20For%20All%20Completed%20Phases%20%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22800%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmid%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20hearing%20of%20the%20turnout%20row%2C%20several%20Opposition%20leaders%2C%20including%20Mahua%20Moitra%20and%20the%20Congress's%20Pawan%20Khera%2C%20had%20red-flagged%20what%20they%20claimed%20as%20possible%20vote%20fraud%20-%20i.e.%20there%20was%20concern%20the%20increased%20number%20of%20votes%20shown%20after%20polling%20could%20be%20illegally%20added%20to%20the%20tally%20of%20any%20one%20political%20party.