nk%5C%22%3E%20who%20started%20a%20cloud%20kitchen%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%98Anjum%E2%80%99s%20Kitchen%E2%80%99%20says%20that%20innovating%20her%20menu%20has%20been%20great%20for%20her%20business.%20While%20she%20was%20known%20and%20loved%20for%20her%20delicious%20homemade%20%3Cem%3Ebiryanis%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20she%20realised%20people%20might%20look%20for%20something%20more.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%20she%20started%20making%3Cem%3E%20%E2%80%98iftar%20platter%20for%20one%E2%80%99%2C%3C%2Fem%3E%20which%20includes%20%3Cem%3Ehaleem%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20%3Cem%3Edahi%20wada%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20fruits%2C%20and%20dates%20to%20attract%20more%20customers.%20%E2%80%9CIntroducing%20seasonal%20items%20like%20%3Cem%3Epanjiri%20ke%20ladoo%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20and%20%3Cem%3Egond%20ke%20laddoo%3C%2Fem%3E%20during%20winter%20can%20be%20good%20for%20attracting%20new%20customers%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E5.%20Spread%20the%20word%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20the%20business%20is%20small-scale%2C%20affording%20a%20marketing%20strategy%20might%20be%20difficult.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERaji%20suggests%2C%20%E2%80%9CWhile%20food%20delivery%20apps%20like%20Swiggy%20and%20Zomato%20can%20help%20you%20tap%20into%20a%20wider%20audience%2C%20it%20is%20important%20to%20take%20some%20more%20steps.%20For%20a%20cloud%20kitchen%2C%20platforms%20like%20Facebook%2C%20Instagram%2C%20and%20Google%20My%20Business%20are%20essential%20for%20reaching%20potential%20customers.%20Always%20ask%20customers%20to%20review%20your%20food%20and%20take%20that%20feedback%20into%20consideration.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E6.%20Treat%20the%20customer%20as%20the%20king%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERaji%20shares%20that%20one%20of%20the%20biggest%20challenges%20in%20the%20cloud%20kitchen%20business%20is%20establishing%20brand%20visibility%20and%20attracting%20customers%20without%20a%20physical%20storefront.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COvercoming%20this%20involves