g.%20In%201878%2C%20Lord%20Lytton%2C%20viceroy%20and%20governor-general%2C%20conferred%20him%20with%20the%20title%20%E2%80%98Raja%20Bahadur%E2%80%99.%20At%20the%20tender%20age%20of%2016%2C%20Rajendra%20began%20building%20the%20Marble%20Palace%2C%20completing%20it%20by%201840.%20Today%2C%20the%20grand%20avenue%20is%20a%20testament%20to%20his%20love%20for%20cultures%2C%20artistic%20prowess%2C%20and%20penchant%20for%20collectables.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EGrandness%20has%20its%20moments%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFew%20are%20fortunate%20to%20be%20privy%20to%20the%20royal%20facades%20and%20interiors%20at%20the%20Marble%20Palace.%20But%20if%20you%20are%20permitted%20a%20private%20guided%20tour%20through%20the%20place%20%E2%80%94%20possible%20only%20by%20applying%20through%20the%20West%20Bengal%20Tourism%20Information%20Bureau%20%E2%80%94%20prepare%20to%20be%20stunned.%20The%20magic%20lies%20in%20the%20chiselled%20details.%20Privacy%20is%20prized%20at%20this%2019th-century%20home%2C%20which%20explains%20the%20stringent%20rules%20about%20having%20visitors.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20a%20lucky%20few%20who%20have%20been%20within%20its%20chambers%2C%20speak%20highly%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F341653%2Funique-homestay-in-goa-maharashtra-sawantwadi-palace-hotel-run-by-royal-family-sawant-bhonsle%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epalace%E2%80%99s%20testament%20to%20preserving%20culture%3C%2Fa%3E.%20If%20you%20look%20long%20enough%20at%20the%20block%20of%20white%2C%20you%E2%80%99ll%20be%20able%20to%20tell%20the%20blend%20of%20different%20architectural%20styles%20that%20have%20gone%20into%20its%20design.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20neoclassical%20style%20Corinthian%20columns%20blended%20with%20fretwork%20verandahs%20and%20sloping%20roofs%20inspired%20by%20Chinese%20architecture%2C%20give%20way%20to%20Victorian%20furniture%20inside%20the%20home.%20The%20roof%20me