0bid%20to%20encourage%20people%20to%20exercise%20their%20voting%20rights%2C%20SP%20Krishnaraj%2C%20the%20owner%20of%20Nisarga%20Grand%20Hotel%2C%20serves%20free%20masala%20dosas%20to%20those%20who%20vote.%20He%20started%20this%20practice%20in%202018%20and%20has%20served%20thousands%20of%20dosas.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Tina%20Freese%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F350690%2Felection-nisarga-grand-hotel-bengaluru-serves-free-dosas-to-people-who-vote-sp-krishnaraj%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Farmer%E2%80%99s%20Startup%20Takes%20Vets%20to%20Doorsteps%20In%20Rural%20India%2C%20Earn%20Rs%208%20Crore%2FYear%20Saving%20Cattle%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20year%20was%202019.%20It%20was%20a%20pitch-dark%20night.%20Jaipur-based%20Manish%20Prahlad%20had%20retired%20to%20the%20bed%20after%20tending%20to%20his%20livestock.%20The%20next%20morning%20when%20he%20woke%20up%2C%20he%20found%20all%20of%20his%20nine%20buffaloes%20lying%20on%20the%20ground%2C%20breathing%20their%20last.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20could%20not%20understand%20what%20caused%20the%20sudden%20discomfort%20in%20my%20buffaloes.%20They%20were%20short%20on%20breath.%20I%20saw%20them%20dying%20one%20by%20one%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20went%20to%20the%20local%20veterinarian%20to%20understand%20the%20cause%20of%20sudden%20deaths%20of%20my%20cattle%20but%20he%20had%20no%20convincing%20answer.%20He%20told%20me%20there%20were%20many%20farmers%20whose%20cattle%20were%20dying%20similarly.%20But%20the%20reason%20was%20unknown%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHeartbroken%20Manish%20went%20haywire%20as%20these%20buffaloes%20were%20his%20only%20assets.%20%E2%80%9CMy%20%3Cem%3Enana%20%3C%2Fem%3E(maternal%20grandfather)%20gave%20a%20%3Cem%3EMurrah%3C%2Fem%3E%20buffalo%20to%20my%20parents%20as%20a%20wedding%20gift.%20Murrah%20is%20considered%20to%20be%20the%20world%E2%80%99s%20best%20dairy%20type%20buffalo%20and%20is%20one%20of%20the%20prestigious%20breeds%2C%20also%20known%20as%20%E2%80%98Black%20Gold%E2%80%99%20for%20farmers%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThat%20buffalo%20was%20for%20our%20breed%20line%20and%20was%20not%20for%20commercial%20purposes.%20Usually%2C%20%3Cem%3EMurrah%20%3C%2Fem%3Ebuffaloes%20have%20a%20market%20value%20of%20Rs%203%20lakh%2C%20and%20its%20pure%20breeders%20are%20sold%20for%20a%20whopping%20Rs%2035%20to%2040%20lakh.%20They%20were%20our%20treasures.%20We%20could%20not%20claim%20insurance%20amounts%20as%20the%20cause%20of%20death%20was%20not%20known.%20This%20news%20broke%20me%20completely%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20laments.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FManish-Prahlad-1716381129.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22With%20536.76%20million%2C%20India%20has%20the%20largest%20livestock%20population%20in%20the%20world.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FManish-Prahlad-1716381129.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FManish-Prahlad-1716381129-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FManish-Prahlad-1716381129-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FManish-Prahlad-1716381129-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FManish-Prahlad-1716381129-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-350777%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EWith%20536.76%20million%2C%20India%20has%20the%20largest%20livestock%20population%20in%20the%20world.%