%E2%80%99s%20needs%2C%20she%20started%20selling%20%3Cem%3Eidlis%20%3C%2Fem%3Ein%20the%201980s.%20Located%20in%20a%20busy%20street%20in%20Gandhinagar%2C%20Pudukkottai%2C%20she%20built%20a%20loyal%20customer%20base%20of%20everyone%20from%20school%20children%20to%20homemakers.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20uses%20ration%20rice%20and%20pulses%20for%20the%20%3Cem%3Eidli%3C%2Fem%3E%20batter%20and%20%3Cem%3Esambhar%3C%2Fem%3E.%20While%20the%20ration%20items%20she%20gets%20aren%E2%80%99t%20sufficient%20for%20the%20quantity%20she%20makes%2C%20regular%20customers%20and%20well-wishers%20help%20her%20with%20their%20ration%20rice.%20This%20goodwill%20and%20her%20benevolent%20heart%20are%20the%20major%20reasons%20for%20her%20pricing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20I%20started%2C%203%20paise%20for%20one%20%3Cem%3Eidli%20%3C%2Fem%3Ewas%20less%20than%20other%20hotels%2C%20but%20it%20helped%20everyone%20afford%20it%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20principle%20is%20the%20reason%20that%20has%20prevented%20her%20from%20increasing%20the%20price%20even%20today%2C%20even%20as%20nearby%20hotels%20charge%20at%20least%20Rs%2010%20per%20idli.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20am%20not%20doing%20this%20for%20profit%2C%20all%20I%20want%20is%20the%20love%20of%20my%20customers.%20That%20keeps%20me%20going.%20Will%20school%20children%20be%20able%20to%20afford%20more%3F%20Everyone%20is%20struggling%20for%20money%2C%20and%20this%20is%20my%20way%20of%20helping%20out%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20the%2084-year-old.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20source%20of%20inspiration%20for%20her%20service%20are%20the%20people%20who%20do%20%3Cem%3Eannadanam%20%3C%2Fem%3E(food%20donation).%20When%20they%20can%20provide%20food%20and%20clothes%20to%20so%20many%2C%20why%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20she%20do%20something%20in%20her%20capacity%2C%20she%20thought%20to%20herself.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20why%20not%20increase%20it%20to%20enable%20a%20better%20life%20for%20herself%3F%20%E2%80%9CLet%20it%20be.%20Why%20should%20an%20old%20lady%20be%20greedy%3F%E2%80%9D%20she%20says%20firmly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20love%20keeps%20her%20customers%20coming%20back.%20Saravanan%2C%20a%20regular%20customer%2C%20shares%20that%20he%20has%20been%20eating%20at%20Dhanam%20%3Cem%3EPaati%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%99s%20shop%20since%20he%20was%20a%20child.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20taste%20of%20her%20%3Cem%3Eidlis%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20coconut%20chutney%20and%20%3Cem%3Ekurma%20%3C%2Fem%3E(mixed%20vegetable%20gravy)%20is%20unparalleled.%20If%20we%20ask%20for%20three%20idlis%2C%20she%20will%20always%20give%20two%20extra%20without%20charging%20for%20it.%20If%20one%20is%20short%20of%20money%2C%20she%20waives%20it%20off.%20All%20she%20wants%20is%20that%20we%20leave%20feeling%20full%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98Help%20me%20build%20a%20permanent%20house%E2%80%99%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20might%20also%20wonder%20why%20she%20continues%20to%20work%20well%20into%20her%2080s.%20Her%20son%20and%20daughter%20are%20struggling%20too%2C%20she%20shares%2C%20which%20is%20why%20she%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20want%20to%20burden%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201345px)%20100vw%2C%201345px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fdhanam3-min-min-1716293333.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221345%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Dhanam%20Paati's%20house%20is%20in%20dire%20straits.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fdhanam3-min-min-1716293333.jpeg%201345w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fdhanam3-min-min-1716293333-300x201.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fdhanam3-min-min-1716293333-500x335.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fdhanam3-min-min-1716293